name: Swa-Sahyog Sanstha
briefDescription: The basic aims of the organization are to promote the development of those sections of our society who are blowing the poverty line & who are unorganized. It tries to create institutions of the people at the gross routs level who will react to the needs of their people in a responsible manner, as well as build up a positive relationship with the government institutions for the promotion of development works.Development Priorities of the Organization:	Livelihood promotion program.	Education program.	Health / Sanitation program.	Focus group development program (Nomadic Community)
